# Routes (`app/**`)

- **Expo Router** file-based routing. The `(site)` group wraps chrome (`SiteHeader` / `SiteFooter`) and does not appear in URLs.
- **Dynamic segments:**
  - `(site)/[slug].tsx` — blog report `slug` (root `/<slug>`)
  - `(site)/podcast/interviews/[slug].tsx` — podcast entry `id`
  - `(site)/legal/[slug].tsx`, `(site)/authors/[slug].tsx`
- Use `generateStaticParams` on dynamic routes so `expo export -p web` pre-renders pages.
- Keep membership routes at `/login`, `/signup`, `/pricing`, `/account`.
